Just open the index.html file to access the website's content. Most of the tests
and demos should work fine loaded from the local hard drive, but some (listed
below) will only work properly from a proper server.

All materials by me are released under the  Creative Commons
Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported License (CC BY-NC-SA), which
you can read more about at http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/.
Materials not by me are documented in the Copyright Information section
of the root page, and are mostly media taken from CC and PD sources.


PAGES THAT DO NOT WORK FROM A LOCAL DISK
- Geolocation test does not work from the disk in Chrome as of version 14.
